spec_data.Name: python3-django-netjsongraph
spec_data.Description:
django-netjsongraph is a network topology collector and
network topology visualizer.
It supports collecting network topology from OLSR,
BATMAN-advanced, BMX and NetJSON NetworkGraph.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sat 29 Jul 2017 12:49:54 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Reusable django app for collecting and visualizing network topology
